data.description: MUST SEE & AFFORDABLE! Better-than-new complete renovation with a new POOL, 3 car garage, and 2.25% VA assumable loan to save thousands every month! This home welcomes you in with an oversized formal dining room, open concept floor plan, spacious high ceilings, molding and fireplace that overlook an inground pool with water features and large, fenced backyard! The living area opens to the kitchen’s all-new custom cabinetry, Italian ILVE gas range, vented hood, quartz countertops, and butler’s pantry for the most discriminating chef! The eating space fits the largest furniture for big gatherings! Open suite off the kitchen includes oversized bedroom, huge walk-in closet and dedicated bath! Four main-floor bedrooms, largest you’ve seen and closets to match! Luxurious master suite and bath you'll always want to wake up to, includes soaker tub, walk-in shower and never-ending closet space! New garden and landscaping! Kingston Benton Schools! Also updated: laundry, lighting, hvac, & roof
